functions.name: AutoComplete (component)
functions.signature: const AutoComplete = ({ options, value, onValueChange, placeholder?, emptyMessage?, className?, autoOpen?, disabled? }: AutoCompleteProps) => JSX.Element
functions.description: Popover-backed autocomplete component. Filters and ranks provided options by label, value, and description. Renders a Command-style list, supports typing to filter, and formats displayed values using computeTermDisplay (via rdfManager when available) with a shortLocalName fallback. Calls onValueChange when an option is selected and supports autoOpen for dialog embedding.

notes: Uses synchronous access to useOntologyStore.getState() inside render to obtain rdfManager for display formatting; designed to be resilient if rdfManager or prefix mappings are missing.
